{
  "video_id": "GMynksvCcUI",
  "title": "Jennifer Granholm: A clean energy proposal -- race to the top!",
  "es": 1,
  "json": [
    {
      "index": 1,
      "start_time": 0.0,
      "end_time": 15838.0,
      "text": "Translator: Joseph Geni Reviewer: Morton Bast"
    },
    {
      "index": 2,
      "start_time": 15838.0,
      "end_time": 18756.0,
      "text": "Well, I was introduced as"
    },
    {
      "index": 3,
      "start_time": 18756.0,
      "end_time": 20788.0,
      "text": "the former Governor of Michigan,"
    },
    {
      "index": 4,
      "start_time": 20788.0,
      "end_time": 23804.0,
      "text": "but actually I&#39;m a scientist."
    },
    {
      "index": 5,
      "start_time": 23804.0,
      "end_time": 26796.0,
      "text": "All right, a political scientist, it doesn&#39;t really count,"
    },
    {
      "index": 6,
      "start_time": 26796.0,
      "end_time": 30592.0,
      "text": "but my laboratory was the laboratory of democracy"
    },
    {
      "index": 7,
      "start_time": 30592.0,
      "end_time": 33748.0,
      "text": "that is Michigan, and, like any good scientist,"
    },
    {
      "index": 8,
      "start_time": 33748.0,
      "end_time": 36590.0,
      "text": "I was experimenting with policy"
    },
    {
      "index": 9,
      "start_time": 36590.0,
      "end_time": 39284.0,
      "text": "about what would achieve the greatest good"
    },
    {
      "index": 10,
      "start_time": 39284.0,
      "end_time": 41393.0,
      "text": "for the greatest number."
    },
    {
      "index": 11,
      "start_time": 41393.0,
      "end_time": 45671.0,
      "text": "But there were three problems, three enigmas"
    },
    {
      "index": 12,
      "start_time": 45671.0,
      "end_time": 48205.0,
      "text": "that I could not solve,"
    },
    {
      "index": 13,
      "start_time": 48205.0,
      "end_time": 51683.0,
      "text": "and I want to share with you those problems,"
    },
    {
      "index": 14,
      "start_time": 51683.0,
      "end_time": 53689.0,
      "text": "but most importantly,"
    },
    {
      "index": 15,
      "start_time": 53689.0,
      "end_time": 57445.0,
      "text": "I think I figured out a proposal for a solution."
    },
    {
      "index": 16,
      "start_time": 57445.0,
      "end_time": 59314.0,
      "text": "The first problem"
    },
    {
      "index": 17,
      "start_time": 59314.0,
      "end_time": 61305.0,
      "text": "that not just Michigan, but every state, faces is,"
    },
    {
      "index": 18,
      "start_time": 61305.0,
      "end_time": 64624.0,
      "text": "how do you create good jobs in America"
    },
    {
      "index": 19,
      "start_time": 64623.99999999999,
      "end_time": 66372.0,
      "text": "in a global economy?"
    },
    {
      "index": 20,
      "start_time": 66372.0,
      "end_time": 69864.0,
      "text": "So let me share with you some empirical data from my lab."
    },
    {
      "index": 21,
      "start_time": 69864.0,
      "end_time": 74374.0,
      "text": "I was elected in 2002 and, at the end of my first year in office in 2003,"
    },
    {
      "index": 22,
      "start_time": 74374.0,
      "end_time": 76906.0,
      "text": "I got a call from one of my staff members, who said,"
    },
    {
      "index": 23,
      "start_time": 76906.0,
      "end_time": 79274.0,
      "text": "&quot;Gov, we have a big problem."
    },
    {
      "index": 24,
      "start_time": 79274.0,
      "end_time": 82894.0,
      "text": "We have a little tiny community called Greenville, Michigan,"
    },
    {
      "index": 25,
      "start_time": 82894.0,
      "end_time": 85156.0,
      "text": "population 8,000,"
    },
    {
      "index": 26,
      "start_time": 85156.0,
      "end_time": 87951.0,
      "text": "and they are about to lose their major employer,"
    },
    {
      "index": 27,
      "start_time": 87951.0,
      "end_time": 92770.0,
      "text": "which is a refrigerator factory that&#39;s operated by Electrolux.&quot;"
    },
    {
      "index": 28,
      "start_time": 92770.0,
      "end_time": 95449.0,
      "text": "And I said, &quot;Well, how many people work at Electrolux?&quot;"
    },
    {
      "index": 29,
      "start_time": 95449.0,
      "end_time": 100379.0,
      "text": "And he said, &quot;3,000 of the 8,000 people in Greenville.&quot;"
    },
    {
      "index": 30,
      "start_time": 100379.0,
      "end_time": 103160.0,
      "text": "So it is a one-company town."
    },
    {
      "index": 31,
      "start_time": 103160.0,
      "end_time": 108088.0,
      "text": "And Electrolux was going to go to Mexico."
    },
    {
      "index": 32,
      "start_time": 108088.0,
      "end_time": 110976.0,
      "text": "So I said, &quot;Forget that. I&#39;m the new Governor."
    },
    {
      "index": 33,
      "start_time": 110976.0,
      "end_time": 113264.0,
      "text": "We can fix this. We&#39;re going to go to Greenville"
    },
    {
      "index": 34,
      "start_time": 113264.0,
      "end_time": 115232.0,
      "text": "with my whole cabinet and we will just"
    },
    {
      "index": 35,
      "start_time": 115232.0,
      "end_time": 118137.0,
      "text": "make Electrolux an offer they can&#39;t refuse.&quot;"
    },
    {
      "index": 36,
      "start_time": 118137.0,
      "end_time": 120568.0,
      "text": "So I brought my whole cabinet,"
    },
    {
      "index": 37,
      "start_time": 120568.0,
      "end_time": 124280.0,
      "text": "and we met with all of the pooh-bahs of little Greenville --"
    },
    {
      "index": 38,
      "start_time": 124280.0,
      "end_time": 127510.0,
      "text": "the mayor, the city manager, the head of the community college --"
    },
    {
      "index": 39,
      "start_time": 127510.0,
      "end_time": 131105.0,
      "text": "and we basically emptied our pockets"
    },
    {
      "index": 40,
      "start_time": 131105.0,
      "end_time": 134398.0,
      "text": "and put all of our chips on the table,"
    },
    {
      "index": 41,
      "start_time": 134398.0,
      "end_time": 138526.0,
      "text": "incentives, you name it, to convince Electrolux to stay,"
    },
    {
      "index": 42,
      "start_time": 138526.0,
      "end_time": 140177.0,
      "text": "and as we made our pile of chips,"
    },
    {
      "index": 43,
      "start_time": 140177.0,
      "end_time": 145284.0,
      "text": "we slid them across the table to the management of Electrolux."
    },
    {
      "index": 44,
      "start_time": 145284.0,
      "end_time": 149392.0,
      "text": "And in the pile were things like zero taxes for 20 years,"
    },
    {
      "index": 45,
      "start_time": 149392.0,
      "end_time": 153608.0,
      "text": "or that we&#39;d help to build a new factory for the company,"
    },
    {
      "index": 46,
      "start_time": 153608.0,
      "end_time": 156401.0,
      "text": "we&#39;d help to finance it. The UAW, who represented the workers,"
    },
    {
      "index": 47,
      "start_time": 156401.0,
      "end_time": 160240.0,
      "text": "said they would offer unprecedented concessions,"
    },
    {
      "index": 48,
      "start_time": 160240.0,
      "end_time": 164293.0,
      "text": "sacrifices to just keep those jobs in Greenville."
    },
    {
      "index": 49,
      "start_time": 164293.0,
      "end_time": 167171.0,
      "text": "So the management of Electrolux took our pile,"
    },
    {
      "index": 50,
      "start_time": 167171.0,
      "end_time": 169984.0,
      "text": "our list of incentives, and they went outside the room"
    },
    {
      "index": 51,
      "start_time": 169984.0,
      "end_time": 172504.0,
      "text": "for 17 minutes,"
    },
    {
      "index": 52,
      "start_time": 172504.0,
      "end_time": 174735.0,
      "text": "and they came back in and they said,"
    },
    {
      "index": 53,
      "start_time": 174735.0,
      "end_time": 177676.0,
      "text": "&quot;Wow, this is the most generous"
    },
    {
      "index": 54,
      "start_time": 177676.0,
      "end_time": 182165.0,
      "text": "any community has ever been to try to keep jobs here."
    },
    {
      "index": 55,
      "start_time": 182165.0,
      "end_time": 185560.0,
      "text": "But there&#39;s nothing you can do"
    },
    {
      "index": 56,
      "start_time": 185560.0,
      "end_time": 189849.0,
      "text": "to compensate for the fact that we can pay $1.57 an hour"
    },
    {
      "index": 57,
      "start_time": 189849.0,
      "end_time": 193107.0,
      "text": "in Juarez, Mexico. So we&#39;re leaving.&quot;"
    },
    {
      "index": 58,
      "start_time": 193107.0,
      "end_time": 196112.0,
      "text": "And they did. And when they did, it was like"
    },
    {
      "index": 59,
      "start_time": 196112.0,
      "end_time": 199368.0,
      "text": "a nuclear bomb went off in little Greenville."
    },
    {
      "index": 60,
      "start_time": 199368.0,
      "end_time": 201683.0,
      "text": "In fact, they did implode the factory."
    },
    {
      "index": 61,
      "start_time": 201683.0,
      "end_time": 205661.0,
      "text": "That&#39;s a guy that is walking on his last day of work."
    },
    {
      "index": 62,
      "start_time": 205661.0,
      "end_time": 209685.0,
      "text": "And on the month that the last refrigerator rolled off the assembly line,"
    },
    {
      "index": 63,
      "start_time": 209685.0,
      "end_time": 212325.0,
      "text": "the employees of Electrolux in Greenville, Michigan,"
    },
    {
      "index": 64,
      "start_time": 212325.0,
      "end_time": 217990.0,
      "text": "had a gathering for themselves that they called the last supper."
    },
    {
      "index": 65,
      "start_time": 217990.0,
      "end_time": 220973.0,
      "text": "It was in a big pavilion in Greenville, an indoor pavilion,"
    },
    {
      "index": 66,
      "start_time": 220973.0,
      "end_time": 225462.0,
      "text": "and I went to it because I was so frustrated as Governor"
    },
    {
      "index": 67,
      "start_time": 225462.0,
      "end_time": 229359.0,
      "text": "that I couldn&#39;t stop the outflow of these jobs,"
    },
    {
      "index": 68,
      "start_time": 229359.0,
      "end_time": 231882.0,
      "text": "and I wanted to grieve with them,"
    },
    {
      "index": 69,
      "start_time": 231882.0,
      "end_time": 235202.0,
      "text": "and as I went into the room-- there&#39;s thousands of people there."
    },
    {
      "index": 70,
      "start_time": 235202.0,
      "end_time": 238945.0,
      "text": "It was a just big thing. People were eating boxed lunches"
    },
    {
      "index": 71,
      "start_time": 238945.0,
      "end_time": 243105.0,
      "text": "on roundtop tables, and there was a sad band playing music,"
    },
    {
      "index": 72,
      "start_time": 243105.0,
      "end_time": 246842.0,
      "text": "or a band playing sad music, probably both. (Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 73,
      "start_time": 246842.0,
      "end_time": 250069.0,
      "text": "And this guy comes up to me,"
    },
    {
      "index": 74,
      "start_time": 250069.0,
      "end_time": 253809.0,
      "text": "and he&#39;s got tattoos and his ponytail and his baseball cap on,"
    },
    {
      "index": 75,
      "start_time": 253809.0,
      "end_time": 256427.0,
      "text": "and he had his two daughters with him,"
    },
    {
      "index": 76,
      "start_time": 256427.00000000003,
      "end_time": 260034.00000000003,
      "text": "and he said, &quot;Gov, these are my two daughters.&quot;"
    },
    {
      "index": 77,
      "start_time": 260034.0,
      "end_time": 263082.0,
      "text": "He said, &quot;I&#39;m 48 years old,"
    },
    {
      "index": 78,
      "start_time": 263082.0,
      "end_time": 267640.0,
      "text": "and I have worked at this factory for 30 years."
    },
    {
      "index": 79,
      "start_time": 267640.0,
      "end_time": 270296.0,
      "text": "I went from high school to factory."
    },
    {
      "index": 80,
      "start_time": 270296.0,
      "end_time": 272904.0,
      "text": "My father worked at this factory,&quot; he said."
    },
    {
      "index": 81,
      "start_time": 272904.0,
      "end_time": 275753.0,
      "text": "&quot;My grandfather worked at this factory."
    },
    {
      "index": 82,
      "start_time": 275753.0,
      "end_time": 280776.0,
      "text": "All I know is how to make refrigerators.&quot;"
    },
    {
      "index": 83,
      "start_time": 280776.0,
      "end_time": 282129.0,
      "text": "And he looked at his daughters,"
    },
    {
      "index": 84,
      "start_time": 282129.0,
      "end_time": 284617.0,
      "text": "and he puts his hand on his chest,"
    },
    {
      "index": 85,
      "start_time": 284617.0,
      "end_time": 287167.0,
      "text": "and he says, &quot;So, Gov, tell me,"
    },
    {
      "index": 86,
      "start_time": 287167.0,
      "end_time": 292495.0,
      "text": "who is ever going to hire me?"
    },
    {
      "index": 87,
      "start_time": 292495.0,
      "end_time": 295928.0,
      "text": "Who is ever going to hire me?&quot;"
    },
    {
      "index": 88,
      "start_time": 295928.0,
      "end_time": 299450.0,
      "text": "And that was asked not just by that guy"
    },
    {
      "index": 89,
      "start_time": 299450.0,
      "end_time": 302128.0,
      "text": "but by everyone in the pavilion,"
    },
    {
      "index": 90,
      "start_time": 302128.0,
      "end_time": 307968.0,
      "text": "and frankly, by every worker at one of the 50,000 factories"
    },
    {
      "index": 91,
      "start_time": 307968.0,
      "end_time": 312280.0,
      "text": "that closed in the first decade of this century."
    },
    {
      "index": 92,
      "start_time": 312280.0,
      "end_time": 315174.0,
      "text": "Enigma number one: How do you create jobs"
    },
    {
      "index": 93,
      "start_time": 315174.0,
      "end_time": 317607.0,
      "text": "in America in a global economy?"
    },
    {
      "index": 94,
      "start_time": 317607.0,
      "end_time": 319907.0,
      "text": "Number two, very quickly:"
    },
    {
      "index": 95,
      "start_time": 319907.0,
      "end_time": 322639.0,
      "text": "How do you solve global climate change"
    },
    {
      "index": 96,
      "start_time": 322639.0,
      "end_time": 326976.0,
      "text": "when we don&#39;t even have a national energy policy in this country"
    },
    {
      "index": 97,
      "start_time": 326976.0,
      "end_time": 331904.0,
      "text": "and when gridlock in Congress seems to be the norm?"
    },
    {
      "index": 98,
      "start_time": 331904.0,
      "end_time": 335066.0,
      "text": "In fact, there was a poll that was done recently"
    },
    {
      "index": 99,
      "start_time": 335066.0,
      "end_time": 339343.0,
      "text": "and the pollster compared Congress&#39;s approval ratings"
    },
    {
      "index": 100,
      "start_time": 339343.0,
      "end_time": 341773.0,
      "text": "to a number of other unpleasant things,"
    },
    {
      "index": 101,
      "start_time": 341773.0,
      "end_time": 345293.0,
      "text": "and it was found, in fact, that Congress&#39;s approval rating"
    },
    {
      "index": 102,
      "start_time": 345293.0,
      "end_time": 348175.0,
      "text": "is worse than cockroaches,"
    },
    {
      "index": 103,
      "start_time": 348175.0,
      "end_time": 355167.0,
      "text": "lice, Nickelback the band, root canals and Donald Trump. (Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 104,
      "start_time": 355167.0,
      "end_time": 359446.0,
      "text": "But wait, the good news is it&#39;s at least better"
    },
    {
      "index": 105,
      "start_time": 359446.0,
      "end_time": 364302.0,
      "text": "than meth labs and gonorrhea. (Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 106,
      "start_time": 364302.0,
      "end_time": 368127.0,
      "text": "We got a problem, folks."
    },
    {
      "index": 107,
      "start_time": 368127.0,
      "end_time": 369765.0,
      "text": "So it got me thinking, what is it?"
    },
    {
      "index": 108,
      "start_time": 369765.0,
      "end_time": 373527.0,
      "text": "What in the laboratory that I see out there,"
    },
    {
      "index": 109,
      "start_time": 373527.0,
      "end_time": 375677.0,
      "text": "the laboratories of democracy, what has happened?"
    },
    {
      "index": 110,
      "start_time": 375677.0,
      "end_time": 378376.0,
      "text": "What policy prescriptions have happened"
    },
    {
      "index": 111,
      "start_time": 378376.0,
      "end_time": 380168.0,
      "text": "that actually cause changes to occur"
    },
    {
      "index": 112,
      "start_time": 380168.0,
      "end_time": 383735.0,
      "text": "and that have been accepted in a bipartisan way?"
    },
    {
      "index": 113,
      "start_time": 383735.0,
      "end_time": 385013.0,
      "text": "So if I asked you, for example,"
    },
    {
      "index": 114,
      "start_time": 385013.0,
      "end_time": 387493.0,
      "text": "what was the Obama Administration policy"
    },
    {
      "index": 115,
      "start_time": 387493.0,
      "end_time": 390607.0,
      "text": "that caused massive changes across the country,"
    },
    {
      "index": 116,
      "start_time": 390607.0,
      "end_time": 391895.0,
      "text": "what would you say?"
    },
    {
      "index": 117,
      "start_time": 391895.0,
      "end_time": 395690.0,
      "text": "You might say Obamacare, except for those were not voluntary changes."
    },
    {
      "index": 118,
      "start_time": 395690.0,
      "end_time": 398231.0,
      "text": "As we know, only half the states have opted in."
    },
    {
      "index": 119,
      "start_time": 398231.0,
      "end_time": 401740.0,
      "text": "We might say the Recovery Act, but those didn&#39;t require policy changes."
    },
    {
      "index": 120,
      "start_time": 401740.0,
      "end_time": 406091.0,
      "text": "The thing that caused massive policy changes to occur"
    },
    {
      "index": 121,
      "start_time": 406091.0,
      "end_time": 408511.0,
      "text": "was Race to the Top for education."
    },
    {
      "index": 122,
      "start_time": 408511.0,
      "end_time": 411753.0,
      "text": "Why? The government put a $4.5 billion pot"
    },
    {
      "index": 123,
      "start_time": 411753.0,
      "end_time": 415199.0,
      "text": "and said to the governors across the country, compete for it."
    },
    {
      "index": 124,
      "start_time": 415199.0,
      "end_time": 418375.0,
      "text": "Forty-eight governors competed,"
    },
    {
      "index": 125,
      "start_time": 418375.0,
      "end_time": 421674.0,
      "text": "convincing 48 state legislatures to essentially"
    },
    {
      "index": 126,
      "start_time": 421674.0,
      "end_time": 423960.0,
      "text": "raise standards for high schoolers"
    },
    {
      "index": 127,
      "start_time": 423960.0,
      "end_time": 426271.0,
      "text": "so that they all take a college prep curriculum."
    },
    {
      "index": 128,
      "start_time": 426271.0,
      "end_time": 431657.0,
      "text": "Forty-eight states opted in, creating a national [education] policy from the bottom up."
    },
    {
      "index": 129,
      "start_time": 431657.0,
      "end_time": 434260.0,
      "text": "So I thought, well, why can&#39;t we do something like that"
    },
    {
      "index": 130,
      "start_time": 434260.0,
      "end_time": 438306.0,
      "text": "and create a clean energy jobs race to the top?"
    },
    {
      "index": 131,
      "start_time": 438306.0,
      "end_time": 440657.0,
      "text": "Because after all, if you look at the context,"
    },
    {
      "index": 132,
      "start_time": 440657.0,
      "end_time": 444635.0,
      "text": "1.6 trillion dollars has been invested in the past eight years"
    },
    {
      "index": 133,
      "start_time": 444635.0,
      "end_time": 446577.0,
      "text": "from the private sector globally,"
    },
    {
      "index": 134,
      "start_time": 446577.0,
      "end_time": 448949.0,
      "text": "and every dollar represents a job,"
    },
    {
      "index": 135,
      "start_time": 448949.0,
      "end_time": 450544.0,
      "text": "and where are those jobs going?"
    },
    {
      "index": 136,
      "start_time": 450544.0,
      "end_time": 452968.0,
      "text": "Well, they&#39;re going to places that have policy, like China."
    },
    {
      "index": 137,
      "start_time": 452968.0,
      "end_time": 454990.0,
      "text": "In fact, I was in China to see what they were doing,"
    },
    {
      "index": 138,
      "start_time": 454990.0,
      "end_time": 457698.0,
      "text": "and they were putting on a dog-and-pony show for the group that I was with,"
    },
    {
      "index": 139,
      "start_time": 457698.0,
      "end_time": 460701.0,
      "text": "and I was standing in the back of the room during one of the demonstrations"
    },
    {
      "index": 140,
      "start_time": 460701.0,
      "end_time": 463064.0,
      "text": "and standing next to one of the Chinese officials,"
    },
    {
      "index": 141,
      "start_time": 463064.0,
      "end_time": 464726.0,
      "text": "and we were watching, and he says,"
    },
    {
      "index": 142,
      "start_time": 464726.0,
      "end_time": 469360.0,
      "text": "&quot;So, Gov, when do you think the U.S. is going to get national energy policy?&quot;"
    },
    {
      "index": 143,
      "start_time": 469360.0,
      "end_time": 472928.0,
      "text": "And I said, &quot;Oh my God -- Congress, gridlock, who knows?&quot;"
    },
    {
      "index": 144,
      "start_time": 472928.0,
      "end_time": 476942.0,
      "text": "And this is what he did, he goes, he says,"
    },
    {
      "index": 145,
      "start_time": 476942.0,
      "end_time": 479679.0,
      "text": "&quot;Take your time.&quot;"
    },
    {
      "index": 146,
      "start_time": 479679.0,
      "end_time": 484317.0,
      "text": "Because they see our passivity as their opportunity."
    },
    {
      "index": 147,
      "start_time": 484317.0,
      "end_time": 487250.0,
      "text": "So what if we decided to create"
    },
    {
      "index": 148,
      "start_time": 487250.0,
      "end_time": 489949.0,
      "text": "a challenge to the governors of the country,"
    },
    {
      "index": 149,
      "start_time": 489949.0,
      "end_time": 492755.0,
      "text": "and the price to entry into this competition"
    },
    {
      "index": 150,
      "start_time": 492755.0,
      "end_time": 496403.0,
      "text": "used the same amount that the bipartisan group approved in Congress"
    },
    {
      "index": 151,
      "start_time": 496403.0,
      "end_time": 499093.0,
      "text": "for the Race to the Top for education, 4.5 billion,"
    },
    {
      "index": 152,
      "start_time": 499093.0,
      "end_time": 501476.0,
      "text": "which sounds like a lot, but actually it&#39;s less than"
    },
    {
      "index": 153,
      "start_time": 501476.0,
      "end_time": 503965.0,
      "text": "one tenth of one percent of federal spending."
    },
    {
      "index": 154,
      "start_time": 503965.0,
      "end_time": 505989.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s a rounding error on the federal side."
    },
    {
      "index": 155,
      "start_time": 505989.0,
      "end_time": 509907.0,
      "text": "But price to entry into that competition would be,"
    },
    {
      "index": 156,
      "start_time": 509907.0,
      "end_time": 513212.0,
      "text": "you could just, say, use the President&#39;s goal."
    },
    {
      "index": 157,
      "start_time": 513212.0,
      "end_time": 516285.0,
      "text": "He wants Congress to adopt a clean energy standard"
    },
    {
      "index": 158,
      "start_time": 516284.99999999994,
      "end_time": 518559.99999999994,
      "text": "of 80 percent by 2030,"
    },
    {
      "index": 159,
      "start_time": 518559.99999999994,
      "end_time": 520538.99999999994,
      "text": "in other words, that you&#39;d have to get 80 percent"
    },
    {
      "index": 160,
      "start_time": 520539.0,
      "end_time": 524189.0,
      "text": "of your energy from clean sources by the year 2030."
    },
    {
      "index": 161,
      "start_time": 524188.99999999994,
      "end_time": 526890.0,
      "text": "Why not ask all of the states to do that instead?"
    },
    {
      "index": 162,
      "start_time": 526890.0,
      "end_time": 528881.0,
      "text": "And imagine what might happen,"
    },
    {
      "index": 163,
      "start_time": 528881.0,
      "end_time": 530869.0,
      "text": "because every region has something to offer."
    },
    {
      "index": 164,
      "start_time": 530869.0,
      "end_time": 533851.0,
      "text": "You might take states like Iowa and Ohio --"
    },
    {
      "index": 165,
      "start_time": 533851.0,
      "end_time": 535868.0,
      "text": "two very important political states, by the way --"
    },
    {
      "index": 166,
      "start_time": 535868.0,
      "end_time": 537756.0,
      "text": "those two governors, and they would say,"
    },
    {
      "index": 167,
      "start_time": 537756.0,
      "end_time": 540471.0,
      "text": "we&#39;re going to lead the nation in producing"
    },
    {
      "index": 168,
      "start_time": 540471.0,
      "end_time": 543073.0,
      "text": "the wind turbines and the wind energy."
    },
    {
      "index": 169,
      "start_time": 543073.0,
      "end_time": 546244.0,
      "text": "You might say the solar states, the sun belt,"
    },
    {
      "index": 170,
      "start_time": 546244.0,
      "end_time": 549944.0,
      "text": "we&#39;re going to be the states that produce solar energy for the country,"
    },
    {
      "index": 171,
      "start_time": 549944.0,
      "end_time": 552114.0,
      "text": "and maybe Jerry Brown says, &quot;Well, I&#39;m going to create"
    },
    {
      "index": 172,
      "start_time": 552114.0,
      "end_time": 554291.0,
      "text": "an industry cluster in California"
    },
    {
      "index": 173,
      "start_time": 554291.0,
      "end_time": 556130.0,
      "text": "to be able to produce the solar panels"
    },
    {
      "index": 174,
      "start_time": 556130.0,
      "end_time": 557779.0,
      "text": "so that we&#39;re not buying them from China"
    },
    {
      "index": 175,
      "start_time": 557779.0,
      "end_time": 559642.0,
      "text": "but we&#39;re buying them from the U.S.&quot;"
    },
    {
      "index": 176,
      "start_time": 559642.0,
      "end_time": 563072.0,
      "text": "In fact, every region of the country could do this."
    },
    {
      "index": 177,
      "start_time": 563072.0,
      "end_time": 567178.0,
      "text": "You see, you&#39;ve got solar and wind opportunity all across the nation."
    },
    {
      "index": 178,
      "start_time": 567178.0,
      "end_time": 571182.0,
      "text": "In fact, if you look just at the upper and northern states"
    },
    {
      "index": 179,
      "start_time": 571182.0,
      "end_time": 573357.0,
      "text": "in the West, they could do geothermal,"
    },
    {
      "index": 180,
      "start_time": 573357.0,
      "end_time": 575669.0,
      "text": "or you could look at Texas and say,"
    },
    {
      "index": 181,
      "start_time": 575669.0,
      "end_time": 579037.0,
      "text": "we could lead the nation in the solutions to smart grid."
    },
    {
      "index": 182,
      "start_time": 579037.0,
      "end_time": 583144.0,
      "text": "In the middle eastern states which have access to forests"
    },
    {
      "index": 183,
      "start_time": 583144.0,
      "end_time": 585468.0,
      "text": "and to agricultural waste, they might say,"
    },
    {
      "index": 184,
      "start_time": 585468.0,
      "end_time": 588069.0,
      "text": "we&#39;re going to lead the nation in biofuels."
    },
    {
      "index": 185,
      "start_time": 588069.0,
      "end_time": 590585.0,
      "text": "In the upper northeast, we&#39;re going to lead the nation"
    },
    {
      "index": 186,
      "start_time": 590585.0,
      "end_time": 593449.0,
      "text": "in energy efficiency solutions."
    },
    {
      "index": 187,
      "start_time": 593449.0,
      "end_time": 596418.0,
      "text": "Along the eastern seaboard, we&#39;re going to lead the nation"
    },
    {
      "index": 188,
      "start_time": 596418.0,
      "end_time": 598237.0,
      "text": "in offshore wind."
    },
    {
      "index": 189,
      "start_time": 598237.0,
      "end_time": 600820.0,
      "text": "You might look at Michigan and say, we&#39;re going to lead the nation"
    },
    {
      "index": 190,
      "start_time": 600820.0,
      "end_time": 604714.0,
      "text": "in producing the guts for the electric vehicle, like the lithium ion battery."
    },
    {
      "index": 191,
      "start_time": 604714.0,
      "end_time": 608121.0,
      "text": "Every region has something to offer,"
    },
    {
      "index": 192,
      "start_time": 608121.0,
      "end_time": 610443.0,
      "text": "and if you created a competition,"
    },
    {
      "index": 193,
      "start_time": 610443.0,
      "end_time": 614561.0,
      "text": "it respects the states and it respects federalism."
    },
    {
      "index": 194,
      "start_time": 614561.0,
      "end_time": 618115.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s opt-in. You might even get Texas and South Carolina,"
    },
    {
      "index": 195,
      "start_time": 618115.0,
      "end_time": 620785.0,
      "text": "who didn&#39;t opt into the education Race to the Top,"
    },
    {
      "index": 196,
      "start_time": 620785.0,
      "end_time": 623186.0,
      "text": "you might even get them to opt in. Why?"
    },
    {
      "index": 197,
      "start_time": 623186.0,
      "end_time": 625737.0,
      "text": "Because Republican and Democratic governors"
    },
    {
      "index": 198,
      "start_time": 625737.0,
      "end_time": 627391.0,
      "text": "love to cut ribbons."
    },
    {
      "index": 199,
      "start_time": 627391.0,
      "end_time": 631705.0,
      "text": "We want to bring jobs. I&#39;m just saying."
    },
    {
      "index": 200,
      "start_time": 631705.0,
      "end_time": 634325.0,
      "text": "And it fosters innovation at the state level"
    },
    {
      "index": 201,
      "start_time": 634325.0,
      "end_time": 636786.0,
      "text": "in these laboratories of democracy."
    },
    {
      "index": 202,
      "start_time": 636786.0,
      "end_time": 641092.0,
      "text": "Now, any of you who are watching anything about politics lately"
    },
    {
      "index": 203,
      "start_time": 641092.0,
      "end_time": 643849.0,
      "text": "might say, &quot;Okay, great idea, but really?"
    },
    {
      "index": 204,
      "start_time": 643849.0,
      "end_time": 646481.0,
      "text": "Congress putting four and a half billion dollars on the table?"
    },
    {
      "index": 205,
      "start_time": 646481.0,
      "end_time": 648754.0,
      "text": "They can&#39;t agree to anything.&quot;"
    },
    {
      "index": 206,
      "start_time": 648754.0,
      "end_time": 652049.0,
      "text": "So you could wait and go through Congress,"
    },
    {
      "index": 207,
      "start_time": 652049.0,
      "end_time": 654625.0,
      "text": "although you should be very impatient."
    },
    {
      "index": 208,
      "start_time": 654625.0,
      "end_time": 662529.0,
      "text": "Or, you renegades, we could go around Congress."
    },
    {
      "index": 209,
      "start_time": 662529.0,
      "end_time": 664087.0,
      "text": "Go around Congress."
    },
    {
      "index": 210,
      "start_time": 664087.0,
      "end_time": 670715.0,
      "text": "What if we created a private sector challenge to the governors?"
    },
    {
      "index": 211,
      "start_time": 670715.0,
      "end_time": 675675.0,
      "text": "What if several of the high-net worth companies"
    },
    {
      "index": 212,
      "start_time": 675675.0,
      "end_time": 680065.0,
      "text": "and individuals who are here at TED decided"
    },
    {
      "index": 213,
      "start_time": 680065.0,
      "end_time": 683593.0,
      "text": "that they would create, band together, just a couple of them,"
    },
    {
      "index": 214,
      "start_time": 683593.0,
      "end_time": 687153.0,
      "text": "and create a national competition to the governors"
    },
    {
      "index": 215,
      "start_time": 687153.0,
      "end_time": 689409.0,
      "text": "to have a race to the top"
    },
    {
      "index": 216,
      "start_time": 689409.0,
      "end_time": 692078.0,
      "text": "and see how the governors respond?"
    },
    {
      "index": 217,
      "start_time": 692078.0,
      "end_time": 696966.0,
      "text": "What if it all started here at TED?"
    },
    {
      "index": 218,
      "start_time": 696966.0,
      "end_time": 699625.0,
      "text": "What if you were here"
    },
    {
      "index": 219,
      "start_time": 699625.0,
      "end_time": 704973.0,
      "text": "when we figured out how to crack the code"
    },
    {
      "index": 220,
      "start_time": 704973.0,
      "end_time": 710419.0,
      "text": "to create good paying jobs in America -- (Applause) --"
    },
    {
      "index": 221,
      "start_time": 710419.0,
      "end_time": 714140.0,
      "text": "and get national energy policy"
    },
    {
      "index": 222,
      "start_time": 714140.0,
      "end_time": 720118.0,
      "text": "and we created a national energy strategy from the bottom up?"
    },
    {
      "index": 223,
      "start_time": 720118.0,
      "end_time": 723569.0,
      "text": "Because, dear TEDsters,"
    },
    {
      "index": 224,
      "start_time": 723569.0,
      "end_time": 726331.0,
      "text": "if you are impatient like I am,"
    },
    {
      "index": 225,
      "start_time": 726331.0,
      "end_time": 729889.0,
      "text": "you know that our economic competitors,"
    },
    {
      "index": 226,
      "start_time": 729889.0,
      "end_time": 733329.0,
      "text": "our other nations, are in the game"
    },
    {
      "index": 227,
      "start_time": 733329.0,
      "end_time": 735681.0,
      "text": "and are eating us for lunch."
    },
    {
      "index": 228,
      "start_time": 735681.0,
      "end_time": 740227.0,
      "text": "And we can get in the game or not."
    },
    {
      "index": 229,
      "start_time": 740227.0,
      "end_time": 744546.0,
      "text": "We can be at the table or we can be on the table."
    },
    {
      "index": 230,
      "start_time": 744546.0,
      "end_time": 746967.0,
      "text": "And I don&#39;t know about you,"
    },
    {
      "index": 231,
      "start_time": 746967.0,
      "end_time": 749674.0,
      "text": "but I prefer to dine."
    },
    {
      "index": 232,
      "start_time": 749674.0,
      "end_time": 759674.0,
      "text": "Thank you all so much. (Applause)"
    }
  ]
}